R.L.D. Associates Limited Partnership v. Inland Wetlands Commission of the Town of Seymour (10345)

Norcott, Poti and Freedman, Js.

Argued February 11 decision released March 3, 1992 Richard R. Ryan, with whom, on the brief, were Annacarina Del Mastro and William J. Ryan, Jr., for the appellant (plaintiff). Richard S. Bruchal, for the appellee (defendant). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
